content.rendered:
Directed by Atul Manjrekar

Written by Atul Manjrekar. Hussain Dalal. Hussain Dalal. Jasmeet K Reen. Athar Nawaaz. Abbas Dalal

Cast Aishwarya Rai Bachchan (Baby Singh (Sumitra)). Anil Kapoor (Fanney Khan (Prashant Sharma)). Rajkummar Rao (Adir). Divya Dutta (Kavita Sharma). Swati Semwal (Jinal) . Siddharth Amar (Vinod :Correspondent). Anaya (Young Girl @TNT). Asif Basra (Vivek Sir).Sushma Bhagwat. Pooja Bhamrrah (Female Host of India Ki Awaaz (as Pooja Bhamrah)). Rajat Bhasin (Jai). Sharanya Chandana (Stylist @ IKA Finale). Yash Chaturvedi (MC@ TNT). Vaishall Naru Chavan (Lady Cop @Climax). Karan Singh Chhabra (Rapper). Sandeep Deshpande (Salesman at Chemist). Sanjay Gurbaxani (Judge). Abudhar Al Hassan (Judge1 @ IKA Finale). Satish Kaushik (Kadar Bhai). Nihal Khan (Random 2 @ TNT). Nihal Khan (Friend). Girish Kulkarni (Karan Kakkad). Amar Kush (Random 1 @ TNT). Indresh Malik (Suraj Kumar). Brahma Mishra (Security Guard @ Baby’s Apartment). Hitesh Mulani (Photographer @ Baby’s Photoshoot). Meetu Nagrani (Judge 3 @TNT). Vrushabh Naik (MC at Sheila Performance).Anaitha Nair. Praveen Pachpore (Judge 2 @TNT). Krunal Pandit (Judge 1 @TNT). Pravisht (Aryan Shy Boy @College). Barbie Rajput (Rhea). Amit Roy (News Anchor). Ankit Sagar (Factory Supervisor). Pihu Sand (Lata Sharma). Roshan Shetty (Sound Engineer). Karan Singh (Guddu @TNT). Kuldeep Singh (Actor friend). Manav Soneji. Sunanda Wong(Female Producer)

Language Hindi

Producers Kussum Arora. Prerna Arora. Smitha Baliga. P.S. Bharathi. Anil Kapoor. Kashish Khan. Bhushan Kumar. Krishan Kumar. Rakeysh Omprakash Mehra. Nishant Pitti. Aditya Singh. Rajiv Tandon. Hitesh Thakkar

Production Anil Kapoor Films Company Network. Rakeysh Omprakash Mehra Picture. T-Series
